imdb.plot outline: Dwayne Tugg and Chugger are a couple of regular guys who provide Tips to viewers in everyday topics such as Cooking, Garage Sales, and Working Out. They also do movie reviews from their basement apartment under Birch Street Video. One night when they are really ripped at a midnight barbecue, Dwayne Tugg decides to run for Prime Minister of Canada, with Chugger to be his Minister of Self Defense.
